FREELANCE Sales Executive for Carpentry & Joinery
Aden Furniture & Wood Factory llc
Location:
Industrial Area 3, Sharjah
Date: 06-05-2014
Salary Details:
On a High Commission Basis
Job Type: Contract
Job Status: Part Time
Categories:
Engineering & Construction
Manufacturing & Production
Aden Furniture & Wood Factory llc
Please see Job Details for Apply instructions
Saved!
Job Details
We are looking for a FREELANCE Sales Executive on a high commission basis for our carpentry to serve as a key contributor to the company marketing strategy. This will include the development of a strategic plan in targeting and acquiring potential customers in the market and to introducing the Company services to the market through cold and warm calls, direct sales, agents, social media and other channels.
Knowledge: The incumbent must have proficient knowledge in the following areas:  1) Sales techniques, 2) Fluent English/Arabic, 3)  Administration and documentation, 4) UAE sales experience, 5) A positive attitude towards making changes where necessary to improve performance Ability to maintain a high level of accuracy in preparing and entering information
Requirements
1) Bachelors in Marketing/Business, 2) 3 or more years of experience in the same field, 3) Own car/Driving License, 4) Own visa. Kindly send your CV to recruit@adenfurniture.net if you think you’re competent for this job.
